= SDL_HasSSE =
Use this function to determine whether the CPU has SSE features.


== Syntax ==
```c++
SDL_bool SDL_HasSSE(void)
```

== Return Value ==
Returns SDL_TRUE if the CPU has SSE features or SDL_FALSE if not.

